{"tid":176333,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"騎士跌落東岸第2","createTime":"2017-03-28T06:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T14:44:10.000Z","uid":73103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd8fb010173f0cf4fbaf8578b096fe09eeb8381","tid":176333,"uid":73103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"對騎士極失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年playoff final隨時入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近幾場防守食左屎咁又多turnover<br />\n戰術又on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係三分線外尻傳亂射<br />\n冇位射就靠Irving 或 James單打<br />\n比人double team 就即刻傳失<br />\n今日對馬刺第三節已經垃圾時間<br />\nJames打到第3節就冇氣<br />\n騎士個底又廢，求其一個勁d 嘅pg突破分球已經猜到空哂，內外都廢到仆街<br />\n東岸playoff打巫師，塞爾特人同速龍打條撚<br />\n簽Deron William,Bougt返黎吹到好勁<br />\n玻璃Bougt傷，Deron融入唔到球隊<br />\n搞到成隊又老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />補位又慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇騎士second round playoff出局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4891a08f03fb8d1f9cc0ef8a792c674c7a86f9a8","tid":176333,"uid":2296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}